				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							The Armani Ballroom is a pinnacle of luxury and sophistication, embodying the exquisite design philosophy of the renowned fashion house, Giorgio Armani. Located within the prestigious Armani Hotel Dubai, this stunning venue offers a captivating blend of contemporary elegance and timeless charm. With capacity up to 335 guests this ballroom is perfectly designed for your big day						</div>
				</div>
