				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
							Conveniently attached to The Ballroom, The Terrace is a remarkable outdoor venue with sweeping vista of the stunning cityscape of Downtown Dubai and Burj Khalifa. With capacity up to 200 guests, we probably have one of the most breath-taking, undisturbed views in all of Dubai of this iconic building.						</div>
